item.title: Supercharge Your TIMM Models: 84x Faster Inference with ONNX Runtime Optimization
item.description: 🚀 Motivation Real time inference speed is crucial for many applications in production. Some could mean life or death. 💀 Imagine you’re behind the wheels of a self-driving car and the car takes 1 second to detect an oncoming truck. Just one second too late… ⏰ And you could end up somewhere heavenly… 👼👼👼 I hope that shows you how crucial this problem is. Today (2024), ML models are being deployed in all kinds of high-stakes industries like healthcare, finance, and self-driving cars.
